OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud soon lifting to
OL,6,Fleave a fine day. After a cool start,
OL,7,Fsoon feeling warm with spells of
OL,8,Fstrong April sunshine despite the
OL,9,Fwind. Sunshine turning hazier later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome patchy cloud returning
OL,12,Fovernight leaving few clear spells.
OL,13,FTemperatures will fall away to low
OL,14,Fsingle figures with a couple frosty
OL,15,Fpatches.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAnother bright and sunny day
OL,18,Fwill follow for all. Turning hazier
OL,19,Ffrom the south through the afternoon.
OL,20,FRemains gusty across the high ground
OL,21,Fof Devon and Cornwall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
